</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_287" id="143r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_287_r1l2"><expan>Rot<ex>emburg</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_287_r1l3"><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / Vns hat Hans von <expan>Perlaching<ex>en</ex></expan> Marloch genant / von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l4"><expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Spieſʒin <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>verſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / darauf vvir Jm ge </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l5">antwurt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd hat darnach er vnd etlıch <expan>ande<ex>r</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> entſo </del> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l6">ſeinen <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> vns entſagt / . als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> vveıſheit des alles </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l7">abſchrifte ſchıcken <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſloʒʒen</expan> in <expan>dıſe<ex>m</ex></expan> briefe / vnd darauf <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l8">ſie die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> angriffen / . Nu <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wıllen ewr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l9"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>mügen</expan> darcʒü tün / vnd fürderlıch <expan>gerat<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>beholffe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein vvöllet / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l10">
<add>vnd <expan>beſeh<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add> ob der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan> lewte die ſie <expan>gevange<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ledig vnd Jn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l11">das Jr <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> werden möchte / vnd daʒ das entſagen vnd die vehe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l12">gen vns abgetan würd / . vnd ſeit <expan>darynen</expan> durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l13">gemüwet / was Jr <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> gütes darcʒü getün mügt / . Als etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_287_r1l14">Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_287" id="143r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Rot<ex>emburg</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns hat Hans von
                                <expan>Perlaching<ex>en</ex></expan>, Marloch genant, von
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Spieszin, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan>, <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>verschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, darauf wir im geantwurt
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, und hat darnach er und etlich
                                <expan>ande<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> seinen <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> uns
                        entsagt, als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> weisheit des alles abschrifte
                        schicken <expan>v<ex>er</ex>slozzen</expan> in <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        briefe, und darauf <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sie die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> angriffen. Nu
                            <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen ewr <expan>v<ex>er</ex>mügen</expan>
                        darczü tün und fürderlich <expan>gerat<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                <expan>beholffe<ex>n</ex></expan> sein wöllet <add>und
                                    <expan>beseh<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add>, ob der
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan> lewte, die sie
                            <expan>gevange<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, ledig und in das ir
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> werden möchte, und daz das entsagen und
                        die vehe gen uns abgetan würd. Und seit <expan>darynen</expan> durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen gemüwet, was ir
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> gütes darczü getün mügt. Als etc. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
